{
  "version": "v2-2026-05-28",
  "description": "Universal (customer-agnostic) over-broad keyword stop-list for the requirement code-name regex baseline. Customer/project-specific broad terms live in a gitignored customer file (see profile.input.scope.stop_keywords_path); generate a draft via contextos suggest-stop-keywords.",
